ithonline\/2014\/01\/17\/umar-islam-ruined\/","url_meta":{"origin":14774,"position":2},"title":"Umar on Islam: Muslims ruined by faulty scholars, leaders, hypocrites","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 17, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ziyad ibn Hudayr reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said to me, \"Do you know what will dismantle Islam?\" I said no. Umar said, \u201cIslam will be dismantled by the faults of scholars, the bickering of hypocrites over the Book, and the judgments of misguided leaders.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18890,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/04\/25\/umar-learn-teach-dignity-humility\/","url_meta":{"origin":14774,"position":3},"title":"Umar on Knowledge: Learn and teach with dignity, humility","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 25, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"'Imran ibn Muslim reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cAcquire knowledge and teach people. Learn with it dignity and tranquility, humility for those who teach you and humility for those whom you teach. Do not be tyrannical scholars and thus base your knowledge upon your\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11611,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/22\/salman-king-not-a-khalifah\/","url_meta":{"origin":14774,"position":4},"title":"Salman on Khil